There are many signs to spot a loan fraud:
➡️ When an advance processing fee is asked
➡️ When your credit history is not verified
➡️ When a sense of urgency is created to avail the offer
➡️ When the loan offer is too good to be true

If you see a lucrative loan offer, do the necessary checks at your end before making a decision.

Watch the video and download RBI's 'Raju & The Forty Thieves' booklet to stay aware and alert! Let's stay united to #BeatCyberFrauds!

➡️ https://bit.ly/3QKo34M
